i, for they feared of Her wrath since Tantras s=\r\ntrictly forbid harming the female of any specifies for a worshiper of the G=\r\noddess. So if blame has to be laid for mistreatment of women, objectively i=\r\nt would not fall on those whose chief worship was of Durga or Kali or one o=\r\nf Her forms.\n\n&gt; \n\n&gt; \n\n&gt; -Regards\n\n&gt; =C3=82=C2=A0Rajarshi\n\n&gt; \n\n&gt; \n\n&gt; Bazeech=\r\na-e-atfal hain duniya mere aage.\n\n&gt; Hota hain shab-o-roz tamasha mere aage\n=\r\n\n&gt; =C3=82=C2=A0\n\n&gt; Ek khel hain aurang-e-sulemaan mere nazdeek\n\n&gt; Ek baat h=\r\nain ijaz-e-masiah mere aage.\n\n&gt; \n\n&gt; \n\n&gt; ________________________________\n\n&gt;=\r\n  From: sunrise_1080 &lt;sunrise_1080@...&gt;\n\n&gt; To: vedic-wisdom@yahoogroups.com=\r\n \n\n&gt; Sent: Saturday, 16 June 2012 12:13 AM\n\n&gt; Subject: [vedic-wisdom] Re: K=\r\narmic liability for Tantra &quot;material sadhana&quot;\n\n&gt;  \n\n&gt; \n\n&gt; =C3=82=C2=A0 \n\n&gt; =\r\n\n\n&gt; \n\n&gt; --- In vedic-wisdom@yahoogroups.com, &quot;scsa_taker3&quot; &lt;scsa_taker3@&gt; w=\r\nrote:\n\n&gt; &gt;\n\n&gt; &gt; First of all, to anyone reading this , please chant mentall=\r\ny while\n\n&gt; &gt; reading, time is running out, who knows when you will reach th=\r\ne\n\n&gt; &gt; cremation ground, chant and chant. For those who don&#39;t have anything=\r\n to\n\n&gt; &gt; chant, please chant ram, waheguru, allah or any name, mentally. Re=\r\ncite\n\n&gt; &gt; any mantra, anything, every waking moment should be devoted to go=\r\nd,\n\n&gt; &gt; because its the only worthwhile thing to do as a human.\n\n&gt; &gt; Bolo h=\r\nari bolo gopaal bolo\n\n&gt; \n\n&gt; Thanks for the advice to chant till the cremati=\r\non ground. Sound advice no doubt.\n\n&gt; \n\n&gt; Unfortunately Durga is partial to =\r\nsome of her children it seems, and not all of us are blessed with the inten=\r\nse desire to chant as you seem to be. Stop rubbing it in please. \n\n&gt; \n\n&gt; Wh=\r\nat is the use of a